  <title>Gio.Notification.prototype.add_button</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function add_button(label: String, detailed_action: String): void {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_notification_add_button()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Adds a button to <code>notification</code> that activates the action in
<code>detailed_action</code> when clicked. That action must be an
application-wide action (starting with "app."). If <code>detailed_action</code>
contains a target, the action will be activated with that target as
its parameter.</p>  <p>See <link xref="Gio.action_parse_detailed_name"/> for a description of the format
for <code>detailed_action</code>.</p>
  <p>Since 2.40</p>
